Finance Director
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/05 13:24:11
Ref. JB3047481
Job Description
We are looking for top caliber finance director to manage all of our finance and accounting as we continue our rapid expansion throughout the Middle East. This person will work directly with our two managing partners and be responsible for building the finance and accounting organization for all of our businesses. We are looking for top caliber finance director to manage all of our finance and accounting as we continue our rapid expansion throughout the Middle East. This person will work directly with our two managing partners and be responsible for building the finance and accounting organization for all of our businesses.
The primary responsibilities include:
• Ensuring all accounting entries are made accurately each month
• Reconciling our accounting entries to our bank accounts each week
• Management reporting for all of our businesses on a monthly basis
• Establishing processes for payments, invoicing, and collections and ensuring they are being followed
• Managing payroll
• Advising on tax matters
• Ensuring that each business adheres to their business plan and does not over-spend or significantly under-spend
Skills
The ideal candidate will have the following skills & experience:
•Top academic background - + GPA from a world-class university
• 6-10 years of experience, preferably both at a Big 4 accounting firm and a high-growth company
• Capable of building a complex finance department with strong processes from scratch, including managing, payroll, A/R, reporting and other key functions
• Excellent communication skills
• Highly motivated & results-driven; willing to work long hours in a fast-paced start-up environment
