About This Company
Middle East Internet Holding is a joint venture between Rocket Internet and MTN Telecom founded in 2013. It is being run by part of the team that founded Namshi.com, the biggest online fashion store in the region.We have recently launched three new internet businesses in the Middle East: Lamudi.com a real estate classifieds platform operating today in twelve countries within Asia, Africa and Latin America, EasyTaxi.com a mobile phone application for requesting taxis, and Carmudi an online portal for vehicles .Our recruiting process is very selective. Management profiles include McKinsey, Google, Stanford GSB, and Harvard business school. We are looking for people who can work side by side with some of the best in the industry.
